          <a href="/results" class="btnPrimary">See our results</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="bg-grey align-middle">
    <div class="ipu">
      <div>
        <p class="prehead">FREE RESOURCES</p>
        <h2>As we learn and build, we share</h2>
        <p>Search is constantly evolving and knowledge-sharing is way cooler than gate-keeping. That much we’re sure of. Otherwise, we’re researching, building, and experimenting to help keep the community two steps ahead.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/resources#tools">ADD OUR CHROME EXTENSIONS ></a></li>
