            Gray Dot Co really knocked it out of the park for us at Osmos. Their approach to SEO and content marketing helped us cut through the noise. They didn't just deliver a cookie-cutter solution - they dug deep, crafted a roadmap that fit us like a glove, and created content that really spoke to our unique selling points. But what really sets them apart is how they've become true partners in our journey. They're not just another vendor - they're an extension of our team, fully invested in our success in this competitive space.
          </p>
          <p>Naresh Venkat · Co-Founder, Osmos</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-testimonial">
          <img src={transformImageSrc("https://assets.thegray.company/f/1016570/120x120/59cec8c56a/melanie-almeida.jpeg")} alt="Mélanie Almeida, Growth Manager, Strapi" width="120" height="120" />
          <p class="quote">
            I had the pleasure of hiring the Gray Dot Company twice. Both times, they demonstrated their strong knowledge of technical SEO and amazed my team and me. They don't sugarcoat results. They takes the time to explain, build reports and write best practices for us.<br />
            The communication between my team and Sam was smooth since they both spoke the same language. I recommend hiring the Gray Dot Company for your next technical SEO projects.
          </p>
          <p>Mélanie Almeida · Growth Manager, Strapi</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-testimonial">
          <img src={transformImageSrc("https://assets.thegray.company/f/1016570/120x120/cab2031148/alex-johnson.jpeg")} alt="Alex Johnson, Director of Consumer Experience, Cherry Creek Mortgage" width="120" height="120" />
          <p class="quote">
            Gray Dot Company provides ongoing SEO strategy and execution regarding content and technical, on-page development. They are now spearheading a nationally focused keyword campaign. Website visibility has increased markedly since the new site launched thanks to The Gray Dot Company's regular communication and holistic approach. Rather than solely focusing on immediate tasks, they also drive long-term planning and growth efforts. Customers can expect wide-ranging benefits.
          </p>
          <p>Alex Johnson · Director of Consumer Experience, Cherry Creek Mortgage</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-testimonial">
          <img src={transformImageSrc("https://assets.thegray.company/f/1016570/120x120/365fc08580/kristen-edgerton.jpeg")} alt="Kristen Edgerton, Head of Merchandising, Artifact Uprising" width="120" height="120" />
          <p class="quote">
            We hired the Gray Dot Company to conduct an audit of our site and help us identify key optimization opportunities following a larger site migration initiative. Aside from the expertise they brought to the table, I was really wowed by the way in which they took that expertise and mapped it to the unique nuances of our site and business. Gray Dot took the time to understand the inherent opportunities and limitations that were distinct to our business, crafting their recommendations and approach accordingly.
          </p>
          <p>Kristen Edgerton · Head of Merchandising, Artifact Uprising</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-testimonial">
          <img src={transformImageSrc("https://assets.thegray.company/f/1016570/200x200/cae25c74b2/julia-taylor-brown.jpg")} alt="Julia Taylor-Brown, Head of Content, Culinary & Engagement" width="120" height="120" />
          <p class="quote">
            Tory and the GDC team are some of the smartest, most professional and thoughtful people I have ever worked with. They have the unique ability to marry incredible research skills and data analysis with a deep contextual understanding of what a company needs from SEO at the particular stage of their lifecycle. TGDC uncovered an exciting greenfield for us to shine in an undeveloped niche, giving us a clear and focused path to follow. TGDC is at the top of my referral list for any company building out or focusing their content program. I cannot recommend them highly enough!
          </p>
